<p>CKEditor will be the default editor in Drupal 8 and&nbsp;is currently the most popular editor in Drupal 7.</p>
<p>However, in some respects, CKEditor isn't very tightly integrated into Drupal. For example, it's not able to access Drupal images or link to Drupal content.</p>
<p>The Linkit module is the best way to improve linking.</p>
<p>Linkit provides an auto-complete field for linking to nodes, users, files, terms, and fields. Linkit makes creating links significantly more user-friendly.</p><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/ostrainingdrupal/~4/dcIlSfpQFN0" height="1" width="1"/>
